- Use the Palmera color palette: Midnight Blue (#1a365d), Palm Green (#38a169), Ivory White (#f7fafc), Sandstone Beige (#f4f1eb), Gold Accents (#d69e2e)
- Use the Palmera typography: Playfair Display for headings, Lato for body text
- Implement consistent spacing using the 8px grid system
- Use proper component variants for different states (primary, secondary, outline, ghost)
- Implement proper accessibility with WCAG 2.1 AA compliance
- Use proper responsive breakpoints for mobile-first design
- Implement proper dark mode support with design system tokens
- Use proper animation and transition timing for smooth interactions
- Implement proper iconography with consistent icon styles
- Use proper form styling with consistent input and button styles
- Implement proper card and layout components with consistent shadows and borders
- Use proper loading states and skeleton components
- Implement proper error states with consistent error messaging
- Use proper success states with consistent success indicators
- Implement proper empty states with helpful messaging
- Use proper navigation components with consistent styling
- Implement proper modal and overlay components
- Use proper data visualization components with consistent chart styling
- Implement proper mobile-specific components with touch-friendly interactions
- Use proper internationalization support with RTL language support